snippet.textDisplay: I once did a favor for an old friend of mine. He had asked me if I could go and pick up his moms SUV from a restaurant parking lot. She was takin to the hospital after falling . Anyways it was in the middle if the day and the temperature was at least 110 to 115 . So after I pick up my wife so she can drive my truck back for me we head out.
